maintext:
ROCKY HILL, Conn. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday afternoon’s drawing of the Connecticut Lottery’s “Lucky Links Day” game were:
01-08-11-12-14-17-18-20
(one, eight, eleven, twelve, fourteen, seventeen, eighteen, twenty)
